      <title>法国部长称支持欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-supports-european-tariffs-on-china-evs-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新任外交部长表示，鉴于北京方面为维持该领域的主导地位而提供补贴，法国支持欧盟对中国生产的电动汽车征收关税的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-supports-european-tariffs-on-china-evs-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
